  "notes": [
    "Choose the weapons your model is equipped with from the following: up to one ranged weapon, up to two pistols, one or two melee weapons.",
    "Dreadnought Crucible Champions use the Dreadnought weapon options instead of the standard Step 4 options.",
    "For Dreadnoughts, first select one of: Ballistus missile launcher and armoured feet; Brutalis bolt rifles and Brutalis fists; Brutalis talons; Heavy flamer and Redemptor fist; Onslaught gatling cannon and Redemptor fist.",
    "Then, if your Dreadnought is not equipped with Brutalis bolt rifles and Brutalis fists, or Brutalis talons, it is equipped with one of: Ballistus lascannon (+10 pts); Heavy onslaught gatling cannon (+10 pts); Macro plasma incinerator (+10 pts).",
    "Then select one of: Twin fragstorm grenade launcher; Twin heavy bolter and twin Icarus ironhail heavy stubber; Twin multi-melta and twin Icarus ironhail heavy stubber (+10 pts); Twin storm bolter.",
    "Finally, if your Dreadnought is not equipped with a twin Icarus ironhail heavy stubber, it can be equipped with 1 Icarus rocket pod.",
    "Before selecting targets for this weapon, select one of its profiles to make attacks with.",
    "* Psyker model only.",
    "** Mounted model only."
  ]
